version_description: Fix issues with built-in comparison charts.
Add support for Dark Mode on iOS 13.
Update comparison results to include the latest iOS devices.
Improve the performance of the CPU and Compute Benchmarks.
This release fixes issues that could prevent the Metal Compute Benchmark from working properly on some iOS devices.
Improve the performance and stability of the Compute Benchmark.
Fix a crash that occurred when uploading benchmark results to the Geekbench Browser.
Fix a bug that prevented benchmark comparisons from working.
Add support for the latest iOS devices.
